Procedure

I can't reproduce this on the playground, sounds like an incr comp issue?

I tried a really dumb search for similar errors in recent issues and found #83836, which to my untrained eye looks similar (and it is fixed). So I'll try asking the reporter if with the latest nightly the issue reproduces too.
Also interested to know if the reporter can repro with other versions
#83836 does look similar indeed and it was fixed before 1.54.0n so that would explain why this doesn't appear in the playground
Bisected the fix to be #83944, so it is indeed a dup of #83836
